融真係鬼佬野黎，英文唔好，咩都無用"},{"pid":"16b04c2ad2e58b46314cf6be276d4bb9fccdccdc","tid":59072,"uid":57313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T15:41:37.000Z","msg":"咁早考無用，張cert有效期3年，如果3年內有掛過牌，就張cert過左期都唔緊要<br />\n<br />\n同埋睇你本身degree讀乜，讀business、econ、law呢啲科就考paper 1就得<br />\n<br />\n利申：銀行HR，專負責上牌嘅野"},{"pid":"4e3a68ef83ecaa7e5a2704f26b7915e7151cd760","tid":59072,"uid":39622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T21:24:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Year1就諗搵工，我欣賞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你考個試寫落cv點都有幫助</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔想到時fg 揾份得萬幾蚊又做到狗咁唧工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n份份entry位都萬凌架喇 考左咩試咁巴閉可以20k起?"},{"pid":"08d4b2c29e99bfa7cbfe88d273cfc151b1d85f11","tid":59072,"uid":46933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T21:27:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Year1就諗搵工，我欣賞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你考個試寫落cv點都有幫助</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔想到時fg 揾份得萬幾蚊又做到狗咁唧工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你應該係考cfa或者其他專業資格<br />\n而唔係依個類似保安牌既考試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a37ad808499912c9044dfa803c9402cdf8be765","tid":59072,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:55:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以先做期貨交易員，累積經驗，再入基金公司做交易員，再累積經驗，再做對沖基金交易員。</blockquote><br />\n最後開個基金狙擊索羅斯"},{"pid":"d4d623b760f68be18e2de71dd4f9d53b4ce16033","tid":59072,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T10:05:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Year1就諗搵工，我欣賞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你考個試寫落cv點都有幫助</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔想到時fg 揾份得萬幾蚊又做到狗咁唧工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你應該係考cfa或者其他專業資格<br />\n而唔係依個類似保安牌既考試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ncfa都大把人有  唔值錢"},{"pid":"d03c245fac6af38ceccc0f25621834f42b2b0077","tid":59072,"uid":8133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:05:27.000Z","msg":"Year 3 先考都唔遲，你有時間研究下algorithm trading 好過，對你將來搵工有好大幫助"},{"pid":"ba6e6f95e1aff6568a63eee2bc0218b5fc588cd9","tid":59072,"uid":60643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:10:05.000Z","msg":"做證券就考1,7,8<br />\n做期貨就1,7,9<br />\n不過bba畢業就咁考1就ok, 但唔洗咁快考，考完唔上牌，過一排又要考過。<br />\n<br />\nbtw,要做呢行就唔好做銀行，去出面d行做識多d嘢。<br />\n<br />\n利申：轉咗行&hellip;"},{"pid":"d0001ab2b6729273ad2bd70287bf64a8ebe7ae28","tid":59072,"uid":54993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:41:48.000Z","msg":"簡單講 : <br />\n唔使咁快考, 出到黎做野先考都未遲, 唔難考<br />\n(因為太早考左, 會過期, 到時又係要再考過)"},{"pid":"d1a715829a96056ed9c10893be2f5b4bd518ec2b","tid":59072,"uid":62587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:46:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可以先做期貨交易員，累積經驗，再入基金公司做交易員，再累積經驗，再做對沖基金交易員。</blockquote><br />\n最後開個基金狙擊索羅斯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f44e49239e3bff3d5aaf4edae80f4055c2487d","tid":59072,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以先做期貨交易員，累積經驗，再入基金公司做交易員，再累積經驗，再做對沖基金交易員。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我已經急不及待 好想玩玩"},{"pid":"9b944841935ff6c7d0ab119d2ab9c4bb79742c4b","tid":59072,"uid":62587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T14:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Year 3 先考都唔遲，你有時間研究下algorithm trading 好過，對你將來搵工有好大幫助</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有啲興趣 不過唔知bba課程有冇<br />\n想自學點入手?"},{"pid":"6f669b58611192817428cfe7a01fc6d9ba7e9da8","tid":59072,"uid":12788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T17:25:35.000Z","msg":"到時搵倒相關既工，可以同公司claim返考試費，咁早考做乜<img 